Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:31.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20\fad(540,0)}下集  「郵件的真相」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.36,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.11,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.58,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.92,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.67,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.30,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.09,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.93,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:09.35,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.65,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.53,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.74,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.41,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.29,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:41.13,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:35.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.11,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:43.58,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:48.92,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.67,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.30,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.09,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.93,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:09.35,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.65,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.74,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.29,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:33.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:41.13,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:35.41,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:43.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:48.95,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:57.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:09.88,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.16,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.49,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:28.42,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}揺らぐ空に昇る朝日から一番星まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.10,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}振り返れば懐かしい景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隣には前を向く君が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:45.62,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:53.83,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:35.41,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:43.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:48.95,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:53.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:57.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:09.88,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.49,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:28.42,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}從霞光中升起的朝陽  到夜空中閃亮的第一顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:33.10,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}回首望去的景色令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:37.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}而身旁是望向前方的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:45.62,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:53.83,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀酸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月這麼忙  還要搞什麼慶生會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是工作的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  dear  四月出生的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這種事有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  大家笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想一個人讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（我絕對選女僕！）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要加油  讓你黃金週過後也想和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候給出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那個地方沒人住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就得舉手投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是有一點點線索也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的委託是調查郵件發信人的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往後就不屬於我的工作範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把該做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你們按約定付報酬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日光浴食堂」的…春季促銷會…通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在正提供特別菜式…請試吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}憑此傳單享受9折優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  你們挺努力的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月學姐  您也來一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長  你在找人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩沒見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們社團的新人  還請多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問要不要試吃一下特別菜式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪個學科的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年級  名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  您這樣我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  京子小姐要去補妝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子小姐  你大受歡迎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全著了道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算做管家服的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知不覺地做成女僕裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才能錯成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  誰都有犯錯的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是她們倆慫恿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都想收進鈴木世界遺產了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木  你在圖書部開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起  給京子小姐化妝都開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  我個人感覺要是身高再矮20公分就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長你也是樂在其中呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉一下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我在圖書部下了賭注
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望它能讓我有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  讓別人看見這樣  會被誤解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被誤解  我覺得也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…如果我這麼說  你會很困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  之前謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是送給你們大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎很辛苦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是HAPPY  PROJECT嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  御園同學你要不要也來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來做這個的話其實很快樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  也就剛開始覺得害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有社交恐懼症  做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但御園同學你應該習慣站在眾人面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  發現歌姬發傳單的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會很驚訝  也會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底還是因為我是歌姬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會照顧生病的我  也是為了這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（放學後有新世界在等著你  牧羊人）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長？  你有女裝的興趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  這是為了發傳單  迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你不要誤解白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎是放不下你  才照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你相信白崎的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善意是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾覺得那都是偽善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我感覺白崎不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她在一起是不會無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是很不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你的樣子更不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太不注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  歌姬在發傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是  但為什麼是貓耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日光浴食堂」要舉辦春季促銷會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學  今天謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你我們非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  明天放學後要來圖書館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有隻非常有個性的貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那貨算是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長你把儀左大人當什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣氛是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你別這樣啊  佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我們還以為是御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過佳奈助這叫法挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：在女人名字後面加『助』，表示對該女人的蔑視，在現代已經成為死語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  那以後就叫你佳奈助了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面你還真是堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按喜歡的叫就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}注：玉和蛋發音同為tama
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是活得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘  這就是儀左大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀左別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學會嚇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利福利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還獻媚  真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照你的印象  繡了貓和音符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為你是歌姬才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的茶是專門為你調配的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗓子好  能讓聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺我還介意這事就太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀同學  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（日出澡堂  優惠券）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打7折…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生寮的熱水管線壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  每個房間都沒有熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是昨晚的彌生寮裡女生的黃色悲鳴接連不斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  為什麼會發展成大家一起去泡澡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓圖書部成員加深感情  不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  筧你喜歡哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼話題會變成這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判決書正文如下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀凪的胸部顛覆了社會常識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  正義的狀況好悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部的狀況好凄涼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說的話那邊的也有罪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎學姐的僅擦過犯罪界線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是無罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了  鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了只是脂肪塊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佳每天都有喝牛奶吃肉  所以沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你們兩位的安慰只會起到反效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志就是懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是你同志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為一年級生  讓我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你又變大了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就帶可以在洗澡時看的書來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來保持你的理性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金週馬上就要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於HAPPY  PROJECT的事  決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀你跟筧很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說  說得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對筧感興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  這氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢~  感覺書才是筧的女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡到處都是書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去過筧學長的家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  筧沒跟你們說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說已經發展到那種地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大醜聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  我們只是鄰居而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他跟我說隨時可以來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去了也只是兩人一起看深夜連續劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人到深夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能迎來筧跟某人在一起的那天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不舒暢的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡的女孩子  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去別的地方玩吧  高峰學長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正筧學長好像在家裡更快活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  明天你能給我答覆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你指那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都想跟你談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你問我的  想要改變自己的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  有一個叫紗依的妹妹  她小我兩歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直生病住院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能去不了汐美學園了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能治好病  一起上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐美學園是一個怎樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個非常好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都過得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也結識了好多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想早點介紹給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團裡舉行了聯歡會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情急之下就撒了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著盡量讓紗依她打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就信口開河了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓紗依知道了事實肯定會失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好繼續圓謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我非常沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很無語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒用到可笑的地步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎你是想在妹妹入學之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將謊言變成現實對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在用實際行動一步步實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還完全不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也還是單方面地接受著大家的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為白崎你在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才會想要幫助你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼白崎你想說的話都說完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天在圖書部再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管筧同學你給我怎樣的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會認真作出答覆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過圖書部的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解到了白崎這個人的天性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都過得挺開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…為我準備的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白崎的提議嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是大家一起想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高峰記住了你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛認識你的時候  不是交換學生證看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大獲成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  你現在的表情跟被豆子槍射過的鴿子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起~唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…圖書部的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  birthday  to  you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  白崎的HAPPY  PROJECT嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  請表達一下你現在的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是太感謝各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺出乎意料的  讓我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份感覺的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然增加了新的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金週過後也要多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝發言！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次生日上得到他人發自內心的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有想到自己會迎來這樣的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起「高興」「愉快」之類的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是另一種完全未知的感情存在於我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我無所適從
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}收件人：牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}我要怎樣才能跟你見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都在你的預料中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}發件人：牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}為你新的啟程獻上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(0,1000)}如果知道了我的真實身份就請來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀左大人  今天請和我一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撓我撓我撓我撓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻  不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想要更多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASE！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園女王說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須服從！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調教！？
